        WAF Ruleset paranoia mode. This is used to select Rules based on the paranoia-level. Enum options - WAF_PARANOIA_LEVEL_LOW, WAF_PARANOIA_LEVEL_MEDIUM, WAF_PARANOIA_LEVEL_HIGH, WAF_PARANOIA_LEVEL_EXTREME.
